212224ba-5e37-4fd4-a6d1-0fbfeb48e7d8.do_description: To make the output, you have to... recreate the blue pattern then add another part on the left, in red.
212224ba-5e37-4fd4-a6d1-0fbfeb48e7d8.grid_description: The output grid size...should match the input.
212224ba-5e37-4fd4-a6d1-0fbfeb48e7d8.see_description: In the input, you should see...a three-part blue pattern against a black background.

6a0d690b-072e-4774-a601-fc1c057cf127.do_description: To make the output, you have to...recreate one of the sections of the 3-part blue pattern in order to turn it into a 4-part pattern. However the newly created section should be in red and should be placed into the empty section of the grid in a logical orientation in order to create a consistent 4-part pattern
6a0d690b-072e-4774-a601-fc1c057cf127.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input
6a0d690b-072e-4774-a601-fc1c057cf127.see_description: In the input, you should see...a 3-part blue pattern against a black background

72ed89c0-c8a3-4383-b92f-5540ed752496.do_description: To make the output, you have to...draw with red color to follow the pattern of the blue section and make one figure with 4 sections that look the same
72ed89c0-c8a3-4383-b92f-5540ed752496.grid_description: The output grid size...same as the input
72ed89c0-c8a3-4383-b92f-5540ed752496.see_description: In the input, you should see...a grid colored black with a blue shape

78116a20-fbdf-4970-a06a-7d725444a1e7.do_description: To make the output, you have to...mirror right side to left
78116a20-fbdf-4970-a06a-7d725444a1e7.grid_description: The output grid size...same size as input
78116a20-fbdf-4970-a06a-7d725444a1e7.see_description: In the input, you should see...one color grid in black

b772b67b-73ba-447a-9ae1-de3852d0f86c.do_description: To make the output, you have to...copy the left arm side of the blue pattern and mirror image it to the other side of the pattern
b772b67b-73ba-447a-9ae1-de3852d0f86c.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input
b772b67b-73ba-447a-9ae1-de3852d0f86c.see_description: In the input, you should see...a black background with a blue pattern

de848069-b125-4c9f-a03b-6406f527d75f.do_description: To make the output, you have to...copy the part sticking out on the right to the left side, but make it red, not blue.
de848069-b125-4c9f-a03b-6406f527d75f.grid_description: The output grid size...same size as the input
de848069-b125-4c9f-a03b-6406f527d75f.see_description: In the input, you should see...a design in blue
